Rating: 3
The cookie you get right after you bake it, and the cookie you get the next day are two totally different cookies. People should know, if they can just wait over night, the cookie will not be this gentle thing, it will be an intense, rich, crisp, flavorful cookie. I would not make the "right after" cookie again. But I will make the "Wait overnight and they are amazing" cookie many more times.

